## Additional Licenses

### Nalana Model Weights
The trained model weights (stored separately at HuggingFace Hub) are released
under the Apache License, Version 2.0. See https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

### NalanaBench Dataset
The NalanaBench evaluation dataset (500 curated prompts) is released under the
Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0).
See https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

### Base Model
Nalana is fine-tuned from Qwen2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct, which is licensed under the
Tongyi Qianwen License v1.0. Commercial use is permitted with attribution.
See https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct/blob/main/LICENSE

### Third-Party Training Data Sources
- YouTube tutorial transcripts are processed via the YouTube Transcript API under
  YouTube's Terms of Service. Synthesis outputs (not raw transcripts) are included
  in the training dataset as transformative AI research use.
- Objaverse data is released under Creative Commons licenses (CC-BY 4.0 / CC-BY-NC 4.0).
  See https://objaverse.allenai.org/
- Polyhaven assets are CC0. See https://polyhaven.com/license
- All other third-party assets used under their respective licenses. See
  data/LICENSE_SOURCES.md for a complete attribution list.
